#Tornado Reports April 24, 2020
@NWSSPC. Some may become severe, with a risk of damaging wind gusts, hail, and an isolated tornado. Another weekend; more tornadoes. Possible tornado continuing north of Greenville, SC. So far, 2020 is the deadliest #tornado year-to-date looking at years since 2008.
. However, a few isolated #tornadoes can't be ruled out. Chances of Thunderstorms tomorrow.
